Day 10: Lead by Example!
🔥 "A Scrum Master is a servant leader, not a boss!"  
👉 Tip: Inspire your team through action. Be the first to roll up your sleeves and embody Agile values.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
